Package de.rwth.i2.attestor.semantics

This package defines the translation process from Java bytecode to an executable (abstract) semantics.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ProgramParser
    ProgramParsers specify how a source code file is translated into a Program that can be analyzed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TerminalStatement
    Terminal Statements are used to model the exit point of a method.

Package de.rwth.i2.attestor.semantics Description

This package defines the translation process from Java bytecode to an executable (abstract) semantics. Program source code is translated into a Program by implementations of ProgramParser.
Author:
Hannah Arndt, Christoph
